{"type": "article", "id": 20837, "title": "苹果酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-18T07:35:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104201VYXNJ06obxl9TtaD.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是产自澳大利亚贝尔萍地区的苹果酒，他们要想纪念两个世纪以前当地的探险家和政客 Archibald Bell 。包装上都可以看到 Archibald Bell 的头像，而酒瓶最外层的纸包装则用了附近蓝山国家公园的地形图。实际上，人物头像的用笔也与地形图非常接近，线条细密而流畅，用疏密关系来表现立体感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150632JX8pjUDKw6f0as7C.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1063\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.98425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150633yBchvaqHz0W3GnNP.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"787\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7287037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150633n9GbDQcomwKE5ruj.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"795\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150634qy9DaUcVB4CPYsg1.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1421\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.31574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}